es"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></s=
pan></div>
<div class=3D"thumb tmulti tright"><div class=3D"thumbinner multiimageinner=
" style=3D"width:492px;max-width:492px"><div class=3D"trow"><div class=3D"t=
single" style=3D"width:152px;max-width:152px"><div class=3D"thumbimage" sty=
