-file-width=3D"426" data-file-height=3D"431"></a></span></div><div class=3D=
"thumbcaption">Right kite</div></div><div class=3D"tsingle" style=3D"width:=
154px;max-width:154px"><div class=3D"thumbimage" style=3D"height:151px;over=
flow:hidden"><span typeof=3D"mw:File"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w=
iki/File:Reuleaux_kite.svg" class=3D"mw-file-description"><img alt=3D"" src=
