<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Duality">Duality</h3><span =
class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a =
href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DKite_(geometry)&amp;ac=
